          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "执掌经纶，调鼎鼐，辅佐乾坤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "官居黄阁近丹阶，调元辅襄位三台。盐梅落落调羹手，舟楫堂堂济川才。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张千上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫，赵普。宋室驾前为臣，官居当朝首相。今日天下，虽已稍定，还有四处，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尚未平靖。圣上意欲发兵讨贼，与老夫商议。怎奈我日夜焦思，一时无策。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看今夜，风雪漫天，不免到书房中，去检阅史书。来"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掌灯，书房去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "有老夫在二堂心中烦闷，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "想不出巧计策扫荡妖氛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "叫张千、张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你与我把路引，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "去到书房检阅书文。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张千，好好看守府门，倘有什么紧急军情，速报我知。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "捡今阅古聊为伴，独坐挑灯暂息眠。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵普下，张千下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "赵普→张千",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
          "edge": "张千→赵普",
          "turns": 3
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 6,
          "白": 5,
          "唱": 2
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.286,
        "dominant_style_family": "二黄",
        "musical_styles": [
          "二黄原板"
        ]
      },
      "scene_feature": [
        0.286,
        0.3333,
        0.5333,
        0.1333,
        0.4286,
        3,
        0.0,
        0.2667
      ]
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "三军莫把黎民掠抢",
        "丞相现在书房上",
        "今夜晚特把你丞相来访",
        "你若是要听讲",
        "依臣见取西川后去上党",
        "倘若是破刘银得了两广",
        "各路若把王师抗",
        "国事明朝同众臣论",
        "圣道如天不可量",
        "孤好比周文王卿比姜尚",
        "定江山扶社稷要选能将",
        "张千",
        "得胜归来定封卿相",
        "日战要将阵图讲",
        "曹彬",
        "步战弓箭护大帐",
        "潘仁美",
        "王全斌",
        "石守信",
        "老皇兄在筵前来斟佳酿",
        "自古道用兵须有胆量",
        "行霸道去仁义万民失望",
        "赵匡胤",
        "赵夫人",
        "赵普",
        "这一班酒色徒不难扫荡",
        "酒过了三巡甚是欢畅",
        "青衣便服出宫闲望"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵匡胤上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江山一统坐汴京，几处干戈尚未平。独坐深宫天气冷，乔装私出访元臣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤，赵匡胤。自从陈桥兵变，黄袍加身，即登大宝。天下虽然粗定，尚有江南、"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两广、西川、吴越四处未平。今夜风雪漫天，因此私自出得宫闱，到丞相赵"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "普府中，商议平定贼寇大事。出得禁廷，好一派雪景！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "都只为边庭上贼兵骚扰，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "在龙床睡不宁私自出朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "但只见半空中降下鹅毛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "好一似粉装成玉宇琼瑶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "孤这里且向前轻把门敲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张千上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侯门深似海，不许外人来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是哪个敲门？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "叫门官休叫我名姓通上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我有言来你细听端详："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你就说来了个赵大郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "今夜晚特把你丞相来访"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你住了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今夜晚特把你丞相来访"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "说什么赵大郎来赵二郎，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "细听我张千说端详："
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "他在灯下看文章。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "丞相现在书房上"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你家相爷看文章，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我也要去听听讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "俺这里是三公府，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "并非寺院与佛堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "何不前去找和尚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "你若是要听讲、赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "你若是要听讲、赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我冒雪冲寒来相访，"
        },
        {
          "character": "你若是要听讲、赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "有机密大事待商量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你既然有机密大事，何不早对我说？也免得费这许的唇舌。你且候着，待我与"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你通报。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请相爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵普上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "外面来了一人，说有机密大事要见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你去问他，是何处的官员，有什么紧急之事？这等时候，才来禀报！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方才也曾问过他来，他说他叫什么“赵大郎”。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦哈哈呀！原来是圣驾到了，快请夫人出堂。开正门，一同接驾。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。赵夫人上。赵普、赵夫人同跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣赵普，不知圣驾到此，有失迎接，望吾主恕罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你等休要多礼，一同平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普、赵夫人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵普、赵夫人同起。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张千，快取茶汤来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张千献茶。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今夜如此风雪，万岁为何私出禁廷？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爱卿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "孤王在宫闱把龙床上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不愿深宵梦高唐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "特到此访贤卿同叙衷肠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "青衣便服出宫闲望"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣启万岁：为臣有一书斋，颇可御寒，请万岁圣驾，到那里闲坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，卿家带路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。张千，掌灯伺候。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君入臣门第，蓬荜又生辉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣启万岁：臣有百花美酒，可以解寒。待臣持壶，臣妻把盏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既有佳酿，寡人自当叨扰。但烦皇兄自斟，何敢烦劳贤嫂？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣受君恩深重，愚夫妇理当孝敬。张千看酒伺候！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿家在此，所看何书？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乃是《论语》。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想这《论语》，乃是幼堂儒子所读，卿看它则甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这《论语》，虽是儿童所读之书，但是那齐家治国平天下，都在上面。非比凡"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "书也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "《论语》虽是儿童读讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "经济权衡治朝纲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一统山河定有方。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "圣道如天不可量"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听一言来心清气爽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "看此书果能够治国安邦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待臣妾与万岁把盏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳皇嫂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "雪夜里在相府同饮琼浆，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "初登基庆丰年君明臣良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老贤嫂在席间亲捧霞觞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老皇兄在筵前来斟佳酿"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣糟糠之妻，何敢劳圣上，以“贤嫂”称之？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "卿道是糟糠妻不下堂，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "孤与卿贫贱交更不可忘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你夫妻比梁鸿匹配孟光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老贤嫂且回避孤有话商量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤与卿家，有天下大事商量，贤嫂且请后堂歇息。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤好比周文王卿比姜尚"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒过了三巡甚是欢畅"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁，万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤好比周文王卿比姜尚"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒过了三巡甚是欢畅"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵夫人",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣妾裣衽归香阁，准备烹茶待圣人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵夫人下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "天寒夜静雪纷纷，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "何故私自出宫廷？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "圣驾何必亲降临？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "国事明朝同众臣论"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿家呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国事明朝同众臣论"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "孤心中恨的是钱、李两王，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "有刘银和孟泉更觉猖狂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "众黎民同受害各处遭殃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "命何人守西川，谁定两广？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "那江南同吴越无人主张。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我朝中哪一个是员良将？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "哪一个韬略广是架海金梁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "还仗着老皇兄仔细参详。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "行霸道去仁义万民失望"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "定江山扶社稷要选能将"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "万岁爷听为臣把本奏上："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "定江山平疆土且莫着忙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "再领兵去征剿江南的李王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "然后再除却那吴越的钱王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "旗开得胜定然是奏凯朝堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "依臣见取西川后去上党"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "倘若是破刘银得了两广"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "这一班酒色徒不难扫荡"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿家所奏，甚是有理。但有良策，应命何人前往？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣启万岁：想那孟泉、刘银、钱、李二王，皆是些酒色之徒，昏庸无道，暴虐"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待人，民心怨恨。若命曹彬下江南，王全斌取西川，潘仁美定两广，石守信收"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吴越，自必旗开得胜，马到成功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此四人之韬略，孤亦尽知。就命卿家，速速遣人，将四将唤进府来。急速着他"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "们，领兵前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张千，速速将四将，传进府来，不得有误。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张千下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少刻四将到来，就命卿家，替孤传旨，不得有误。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张千引曹彬、石守信、王全斌、潘仁美同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹彬、石守信、王全斌、潘仁美",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江山本是将军定，还得将军定太平。深夜相爷传谕唤，同到相府请令行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四将到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣驾在此，你等向前见驾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹彬、石守信、王全斌、潘仁美",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣等见驾，愿吾皇万岁，万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众卿少礼平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹彬、石守信、王全斌、潘仁美",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众卿到此，丞相代孤传旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵普，今奉圣上谕旨，命曹彬带领五千人马，征剿江南，不得有误！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹彬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "石守信，带领五千人马，攻打吴越，不得有误！"
        },
        {
          "character": "石守信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王全斌收取西川，须要小心！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王全斌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘仁美，扫荡两广，须要在意！"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘仁美",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明日校场，点动人马，即速兴兵前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹彬、石守信、王全斌、潘仁美",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣等，蒙圣上洪恩录用，当效犬马之劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众卿站立两厢，听寡人道来："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "众卿进前听旨降，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孤王言来记心旁："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "兵机战策在腹中藏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "夜战须把锣鼓扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "水战随风使帆桨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "扫灭妖氛理应当。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "休污民妻烧损民房。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "凌烟阁上美名扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自古道用兵须有胆量"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "日战要将阵图讲"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "步战弓箭护大帐"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "各路若把王师抗"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
